,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:05:20.000Z","msg":"俾錢基金佬 仲要自己出自己份糧 洗曬自己份糧先開始賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有百幾萬 買公用股每年都十幾萬息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b858fe2abecd33671d0b7d1e3e6e54dd4f9072c1","tid":1056828,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16588e986399a9a223db3ba79e01769f61cb804a","tid":1056828,"uid":90863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"廢老講到錢個時永遠最醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"依d時間佢仲好數口過你... 想在班有錢老野身上搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e85c44b829acbe2adf8f3ec039c45a4ea2ea11","tid":1056828,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"廢老成日飲茶個陣開口埋口話政府點好支那園勁廢青點衰點廢都好<br />\n一講到錢就英美澳紐加日行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721e836e23a95269b3e0c0d63ee0d63f07a77507","tid":1056828,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"傻鳩先會買呢啲<br />\n死撚左舊錢就俾分佬食左<br />\n我要穩定收入買港燈唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af3fbbc7d8188f7bc493ea85433302f35b86423","tid":1056828,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5e85c44b829acbe2adf8f3ec039c45a4ea2ea11","tid":1056828,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"廢老成日飲茶個陣開口埋口話政府點好支那園勁廢青點衰點廢都好<br />\n一講到錢就英美澳紐加日行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" 